name: Small ID Bracelet
description:
Have your, your boyfriend's or your child's name engraved on this small ID bracelet.  Wear just one or multiple.  Snakeskin, crocodile and lizard options with a pewter plaque.  Have it engraved yourself or order it engraved for an additional $25. Easy snap closure.  1 1/2cm tall and 7.5" circumference.  

* If you would like for us to engrave the ID bracelet for you, please email the initials to: amanda@violetandvalentine.com 

Please note that due to the nature of exotic skins, no two pieces are exactly alike.  Most items are made to order, so orders can take 2-3 weeks to ship.  Email us if you are interested in a special order.  

Made in the USA.
